{"TopicId":111158,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Ask the Mods questions about the Forums!","CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-28T17:01:51Z","PageNum":140,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-17T23:55:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223380945\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221526600972\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022188455\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ho Lam Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, Ho Lam Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do you add a signature to your posts? I just got a circumnavigator badge and now I want to put it in my signature.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Screenshotat20171104.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022433\u0022 src=\u0022http://u.cubeupload.com/Geonovast/Screenshotat20171104.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ho Lam Kerman","CreatedById":188455,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-17T23:56:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223380948\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221526601321\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://u.cubeupload.com/Geonovast/Screenshotat20171104.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Screenshotat20171104.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 height=\u0022433\u0022 src=\u0022http://u.cubeupload.com/Geonovast/Screenshotat20171104.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you! I\u0027ll go add my badge now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Whirligig Girl","CreatedById":36077,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-17T23:59:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223380938\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221526599848\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022157121\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gordon Fecyk\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n28 minutes ago, Gordon Fecyk said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/36077-gregroxmun/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002236077\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/36077-gregroxmun/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@GregroxMun\u003C/a\u003E granted me edit permissions in his repository earlier today, but I don\u0027t want to think of it as \u0027owning\u0027 the mod. I\u0027ve pinged him here to see what he wants. After this I think he wants to take a break from it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou should create your own thread, with a link on both threads to each other.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gordon Fecyk","CreatedById":157121,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-18T00:04:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223380952\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221526601570\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002236077\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022GregroxMun\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, GregroxMun said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou should create y\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Eour ow\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003En threa\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Ed\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat answers that question, then. Ok, no worries everyone.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-18T00:32:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGlad that\u0027s ironed out, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/36077-gregroxmun/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002236077\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/36077-gregroxmun/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@GregroxMun\u003C/a\u003E and \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/157121-gordon-fecyk/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022157121\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/157121-gordon-fecyk/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Gordon Fecyk\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CatastrophicFailure","CreatedById":57438,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-25T22:50:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey, um, maybe it\u2019s just cuz I\u2019m on mobile, but I seemed to have lost the ability to search within a \u003Ci\u003Especific\u003C/i\u003E thread? There\u2019s a search button at the top of the page, but it only seems to let me search the entire forum, or very broad selections like tags or members. Didn\u2019t used to be like this..?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-27T07:22:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there any reason the amount of likes we can hand out is capped?\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 There are so many good posts on here, and they all deserve love, but apparently I only have so much love to offer.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 I think your own rep goes up a bit when you like something else, but seeing as rep does nothing really, I don\u0027t see why we can\u0027t up the limit some (double?).\u00A0 Or make a sliding scale, 0-20 posts X likes, 20-100 posts Y likes, 100\u002B posts Z likes.\u00A0\u00A0 Dunno if that\u0027s compatible with the forum engine though.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-05-27T07:24:14Z\u0022 title=\u002205/27/2018 07:24  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EMay 27, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Gargamel\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-27T22:03:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are people who abuse the rep system, so the rate at which points can be given has a limit. And that limit has already been raised once, so it\u0027s not likely to be raised again.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sarbian","CreatedById":57146,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-27T22:10:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, please keep your interest for post limited.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaxZhao","CreatedById":161618,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-28T10:38:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmm, say if i request my account to be deleted, would you fulfil that?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr can I sue TakeTwo and use the money to pay for my college fee? I think 20mil is probably enough.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBTW EU here\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-05-28T10:38:26Z\u0022 title=\u002205/28/2018 10:38  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EMay 28, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by MaxZhao\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-28T15:02:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223387726\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221527503892\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161618\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MaxZhao\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, MaxZhao said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmm, say if i request my account to be deleted, would you fulfil that?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr can I sue TakeTwo and use the money to pay for my college fee? I think 20mil is probably enough.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBTW EU here\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nForum accounts contain no personal information unless you added it yourself. If you did add those details, it\u0027s simple to remove them without needing a moderator to do so.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-28T15:45:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223387482\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221527458624\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are people who abuse the rep system, so the rate at which points can be given has a limit. And that limit has already been raised once, so it\u0027s not likely to be raised again.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u0027t imagine any forum user abusing the rep system... \u003Cimg alt=\u0022\u0026lt;_\u0026lt;\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_dry.png\u0022 title=\u0022\u0026lt;_\u0026lt;\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"XB-70A","CreatedById":144985,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-31T01:34:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust a little one: I discovered today\u00A0that my account was reported as logged in some hours earlier while I did not connect for the last three days. I just looked at the \u0022Recently Used Devices\u0022 but it only shows information about the last log in.\u00A0Would there be a way in the user account to access an archive of others\u00A0recent connections?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-05-31T01:35:53Z\u0022 title=\u002205/31/2018 01:35  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EMay 31, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by XB-70A\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EWords mistake...\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaxZhao","CreatedById":161618,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-02T16:00:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223387840\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221527519769\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262955\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Deddly\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/28/2018 at 4:02 PM, Deddly said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nForum accounts contain no personal information unless you added it yourself. If you did add those details, it\u0027s simple to remove them without needing a moderator to do so.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027re saying what you THINK, not what\u0027s TRUE. The EU Data Protection Reform\u00A0Art. 4 (1) dictates that people\u00A0have the right to have their information, INCLUDING\u00A0my email address erased if I wanted to, unless you are legally required to store them. Which people\u00A0currently cannot do.\u00A0If TakeTwo expect to bind players and forum users with their\u00A0EULA and forum rules maybe you\u0027re expected to comply with the law?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-02T16:47:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223391382\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221527955222\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161618\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MaxZhao\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n46 minutes ago, MaxZhao said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027re saying what you THINK, not what\u0027s TRUE.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nActually, everything I said was true. You don\u0027t need a moderator to remove your email address from your account. Go ahead and try it, it\u0027s accessible in your profile.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klesh","CreatedById":110814,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-02T19:20:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223391399\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221527958067\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262955\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Deddly\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Deddly said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou don\u0027t need a moderator to remove your email address from your account. Go ahead and try it, it\u0027s accessible in your profile.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut an email address \u003Cem\u003Eis\u003C/em\u003E required to replace whatever the one you\u0027re currently using.\u00A0 So, it appears its not possible to have an account here without an associated email address?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith having to re-activate your account with the new email, it would appear you cannot simply supply a fake email address i.e email @ email.com\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00222AyIf70.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022355\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/2AyIf70.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-06-02T19:22:07Z\u0022 title=\u002206/02/2018 07:22  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EJune 2, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by klesh\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-02T19:39:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223391382\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221527955222\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161618\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MaxZhao\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, MaxZhao said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0INCLUDING\u00A0my email address erased if I wanted to, unless you are legally required to store them.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo tell you the true (emphasis are mine).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#000000;font-size:16px;text-align:justify;\u0022\u003EIn particular, a data subject should have the right to have his or her personal data erased and no longer processed \u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Ewhere the personal data are no longer necessary in relation to the purposes for which they are collected \u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003Eor otherwise processed, where a data subject has withdrawn his or her consent or objects to the processing of personal data concerning him or her, or where the processing of his or her personal data does not otherwise comply with this Regulation.\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSource (item 65):\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/en/TXT/HTML/?uri=CELEX:32016R0679\u0026amp;from=en\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/en/TXT/HTML/?uri=CELEX:32016R0679\u0026amp;from=en\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd, also, from the Article 17 from the same link \u0022Right to erasure (\u2018right to be forgotten\u2019)\u0022:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#000000;font-size:16px;text-align:justify;\u0022\u003E\n3.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0Paragraphs 1 and 2 shall not apply to the extent that processing is necessary:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ctable border=\u00220\u0022 cellpadding=\u00220\u0022 cellspacing=\u00220\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\u0022 width=\u0022100%\u0022\u003E\u003Ccolgroup\u003E\u003Ccol width=\u00224%\u0022\u003E\u003Ccol width=\u002296%\u0022\u003E\u003C/colgroup\u003E\u003Ctbody style=\u0022font-size:inherit;\u0022\u003E\u003Ctr style=\u0022font-size:inherit;\u0022\u003E\u003Ctd style=\u0022font-size:inherit;\u0022 valign=\u0022top\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022font-size:inherit;text-align:justify;\u0022\u003E\n(d)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022font-size:inherit;\u0022 valign=\u0022top\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022font-size:inherit;text-align:justify;\u0022\u003E\nfor archiving purposes in the public interest, scientific or historical research purposes or statistical purposes in accordance with Article 89(1) in so far as the right referred to in paragraph\u00A01 is likely to render impossible or seriously impair the achievement of the objectives of that processing; or\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003C/tr\u003E\u003C/tbody\u003E\u003C/table\u003E\u003Ctable border=\u00220\u0022 cellpadding=\u00220\u0022 cellspacing=\u00220\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\u0022 width=\u0022100%\u0022\u003E\u003Ccolgroup\u003E\u003Ccol width=\u00224%\u0022\u003E\u003Ccol width=\u002296%\u0022\u003E\u003C/colgroup\u003E\u003Ctbody style=\u0022font-size:inherit;\u0022\u003E\u003Ctr style=\u0022font-size:inherit;\u0022\u003E\u003Ctd style=\u0022font-size:inherit;\u0022 valign=\u0022top\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022font-size:inherit;text-align:justify;\u0022\u003E\n(e)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022font-size:inherit;\u0022 valign=\u0022top\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022font-size:inherit;text-align:justify;\u0022\u003E\nfor the establishment, exercise or defence of legal claims.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003C/tr\u003E\u003C/tbody\u003E\u003C/table\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPerhaps it can be\u00A0claimed that KSP forum is of public interest. But for sure they can claim they need the email address to guarantee Authorial Rights. Each post here is, by law, Copyrighted by the author - and since the Forum TOS specifies that the Author\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Emust\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0grant the Forum rights over the material, Forum needs to track the authorship of each post.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-02T19:43:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223391470\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221527967221\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110814\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klesh\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 minutes ago, klesh said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut an email address \u003Cem\u003Eis\u003C/em\u003E required to replace whatever the one you\u0027re currently using.\u00A0 So, it appears its not possible to have an account here without an associated email address?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith having to re-activate your account with the new email, it would appear you cannot simply supply a fake email address i.e email @ email.com\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/2AyIf70.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u00222AyIf70.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 height=\u0022355\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/2AyIf70.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUnless something recently changed, you should be able to just put in \u003Ca href=\u0022/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection\u0022 class=\u0022__cf_email__\u0022 data-cfemail=\u0022accec0cdc4cec0cdc4cec0cdc4ecdbc4cdd8c9dac9de82e582cdc182d8c3d8cdc0c0d582c1cdc7c5c2cb82d8c4c5df82d9dc\u0022\u003E[email\u0026#160;protected]\u003C/a\u003E in there. It shouldn\u0027t send out a confirmation email as far as I know\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klesh","CreatedById":110814,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-02T19:52:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223391484\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221527968580\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262955\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Deddly\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, Deddly said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUnless something recently changed, you should be able to just put in \u003Ca href=\u0022/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection\u0022 class=\u0022__cf_email__\u0022 data-cfemail=\u002230525c5158525c5158525c51587047585144554655421e791e515d1e445f44515c5c491e5d515b595e571e445859431e4540\u0022\u003E[email\u0026#160;protected]\u003C/a\u003E in there. It shouldn\u0027t send out a confirmation email as far as I know\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just gave it a try:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022VlkC1ON.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022525\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/VlkC1ON.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFortunately I was able to use the Change Email Address button again to change it back to my actual email address, and confirmed it in my inbox via link. Back to square 1 then.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-06-02T19:54:17Z\u0022 title=\u002206/02/2018 07:54  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EJune 2, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by klesh\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-02T20:01:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/110814-klesh/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022110814\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/110814-klesh/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@klesh\u003C/a\u003E Oh right, then it has changed. Thanks for testing that. I\u0027m sure we wouldn\u0027t quibble about it if someone wanted us to remove their email address from the system. It would mean they can\u0027t log on, though, so it\u0027s effectively a ban.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-02T20:11:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe should probably wait for word from the Legal department, though, since we\u0027re not trained as lawyers.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-03T09:19:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223391495\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221527969678\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262955\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Deddly\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 hours ago, Deddly said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would mean they can\u0027t log on, though, so it\u0027s effectively a ban.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are free sites, usually found by googling ten minute mail, that literally set those up, email addresses that are valid for only ten minutes.\u00A0 They are specifically designed for this type\u00A0 of scenario, where you don\u0027t want to provide a real email, but need to click on a confirmation link.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor those who are paranoid enough (I do use them from time to time), I would suggest using that to change your email until the legal team gets back to us.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo note though, once that address has expired, you cannot regain access to it, so if you lose your password or something that requires the forums to send another confirmation link later, you\u0027re SOL.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s also very easy to setup a gmail account that contains no personal info at all, with no connections to your real identity (set it up from an anonymous public computer if you\u0027re really paranoid about them connecting the dots), that you will will always have access to.\u00A0 I\u0027m pretty sure this forum account is setup using my semi-anonymous gaming email.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-06-03T09:21:39Z\u0022 title=\u002206/03/2018 09:21  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EJune 3, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Gargamel\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-03T09:21:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223391795\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528017547\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo note though, once that address has expired, you cannot regain access to it, so if you lose your password or something that requires the forums to send another confirmation link later, you\u0027re SOL.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s what I mean. Removing or scrambling the email address would be to effectively ban the person unless he knows the email address and never forgets it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-03T20:39:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlease don\u0027t turn this thread into yet another rehash of the EULA/privacy/GDPR argument. There are already places to discuss that \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/172119-updated-terms-notice-privacy-policy/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehere\u003C/a\u003E and \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/175407-unity-analytics-and-the-gdpr/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehere\u003C/a\u003E.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ultimate Steve","CreatedById":161505,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-04T05:26:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there a setting for the \u0022ping\u0022 sound? Since the update I haven\u0027t gotten it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}